  </data>
  <data name="AboutNanoStore.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>NanoStore is a lightweight, mini app-store–style system originally developed by Alex and later merged into GeekHub through GitHub repositories. It is inspired by the concept of the Windows 8 Store, but designed in a much smaller and simpler form, focusing on fast browsing, easy installation, and lightweight distribution of apps or tools. Unlike full-scale marketplaces, NanoStore is intended for local or community-based use.</value>
  </data>
